By: Tauler
---
Where the mind is busied with images, time must necessarily enter into the
operations of the imagination, and this has no place in the highest school of
the Holy Spirit; for there neither time nor images can help us, but contact is
all that is needed, the which may happen without time within the space of a
moment.
